96:    * (which support configurable attributes). To handle those expressions, see {@link
97:    * com.google.devtools.build.lib.packages.BuildType#convertFromBuildLangType}.
98:    *
99:    * @param x The Starlark value to convert.
100:    * @param what An object whose toString method returns a description of the purpose of x.
